** [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/7075_aluminium_alloy Aluminum 7075-T6] [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23976 Pull request #23976]
** Updated [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/6061_aluminium_alloy Aluminum 6061-T6] [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/23977 Pull request #23977]
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Part Workbench ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Further Part improvements ===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The [[Image:Part_ToleranceSet.svg|24px]] [[Part_ToleranceSet|Set Tolerance]] tool was added to allow the creation of parametric copies of the selected objects with all contained tolerances set to at least a certain minimum value. Moreover, the [[Image:Part_CheckGeometry.svg|24px]] [[Part_CheckGeometry|Check geometry]] tool now includes output about tolerances in the Shape Content tab. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17214 Pull request #17214]
* The [[Image:Part_CheckGeometry.svg|24px]] [[Part_CheckGeometry|Check geometry]] tool now also has results entries for valid shapes, shows skipped objects and generates reports in the [[Report_view|report view]]. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/17631 Pull request #17631]
* [[Image:Part_Loft.svg|24px]] [[Part_Loft|Loft]] and [[Image:Part_Sweep.svg|24px]] [[Part_Sweep|Sweep]] now create solids by default. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22098 Pull request #22098]
* The redundant [[Image:Part_Import.svg|24px]] [[Part_Import|Part Import]] and [[Image:Part_Export.svg|24px]] [[Part_Export|Part Export]] tools were removed from the menu. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/22116 Pull request #22116]
</div>

